{"tid":476689,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Uber逾五千萬乘客資料被盜　付十萬美元予黑客銷毀  1年後才公布","createTime":"2017-11-22T08:33:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T09:20:32.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4db8a06f64957d5ee3435ce0ca0003720df5cb6e","tid":476689,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:33:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1366155-20171122.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1366155-20171122.htm&d=iZ8SjhuwUcEPij6oaX2b4O9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=81e29c3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1366155-20171122.htm&h=afe464eb\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1366155-20171122.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1366155_1_20171122084801.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1366155_1_20171122084801.jpg&h=6df8f08a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n手機應用程式Uber表示，一年前被黑客入侵，有5700萬名乘客及司機的資料被盜，其後向黑客繳付10萬美元款項，將資料銷毀。<br />\n<br />\nUber表示，被盜的檔案包括乘客的姓名、電郵地址及電話號碼，以及大約60萬名司機的姓名及駕駛執照資料。公司表示，暫時無證據顯示，被盜資料被其他人利用。<br />\n<br />\n近月接任Uber行政總裁的霍斯勞沙希表示，對於公司當時沒有公開事件向客戶交代，亦存有疑問，當得悉事件後，已要求全面調查事發經過及公司處理手法。"},{"pid":"7188e813eb0ee5455d61039b158c816ee1b741d1","tid":476689,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T09:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}